                    overlayDescription="Hear from some of the scientists who are helping discover and build new chemical compounds."
                    overlayHeading="Concept to Care"
                    placeholderImage="https://delivery-p157365-e1665873.adobeaemcloud.com/adobe/assets/urn:aaid:aem:659384ff-e028-472e-a016-3f1daa5315e4/as/how-medicinal-chemists-are-creating-yt-screenshot.jpg"
